00:20:46.845 --> 00:20:48.813 align:start size:94% position:6%
and help people understand
the plight of sharks.

00:20:48.813 --> 00:20:51.916
So all of this sort of
prelude brings me to

00:20:51.916 --> 00:20:54.853 align:start size:97% position:3%
